# Search

## Building an Index

```
jaringan-browser index ./my-site --output search.idx
```

## Searching

```
jaringan-browser search ./my-site "query terms"
```

## In-Browser Search

```
? q label="Search" placeholder="Type here..."
! search label="Search" method="POST" target="/actions/search" auth="demo-search"
```

